creator: Printbox
descriptionHtml:
Printbox is a native mobile application to create photo products. This is simplified and more automated version of the editor and is a part of a complete Printbox package for photo products. Users get to use the most important functionalities to create their personalized photo products on an easy-to-use mobile experience.

The app itself contains a demo version which simulates major functionalities without a connection to a production module. It means that you can test the app, create your personalized photo product and order it, but it won't be printed and shipped to you.

Printbox App is available in demo version to show what the app can really do for your customers. Full version can be launched for you with your branding to cover photo product sales on mobile devices.

Key Features:

Create and order photo products anytime, anywhere

Upload your smartphone photos to Printbox - quickly and easily

Available for all Android tablets and smartphones

Safe and secure checkout


More information about Printbox: http://getprintbox.com/

Live demo of an online editor: http://demo.getprintbox.com/en/

Email us with any questions at: info@getprintbox.com
